#summary is_contradiction(F)
is_contradiction(F)
<pre>
inputs: F is a formula.
return: whether F is a contradiction or not.
</pre>
| `let x`,,1,,`, ..., x`,,n,,` be the free variables in F`
| `return whether `[RewriterSimplify R_simplify]`(`[RewriterQuantifierElimination R_quantifier_elimination]`( there exists x`,,1,,` : ... there exists x`,,n,,` : F )) is "False"`
